Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要正式抗议一次\NI want to register a formal protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}知道了\NNoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你考虑周全了吗\NHave you thought of everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然没有\NCourse not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没必要考虑自取灭亡的事\NIt doesn't occur to me how to engineer my own destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们这样穿过了密苏里河\NWe crossed the Missouri like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那条河比克劳河更宽广\Ngreater river than the Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那时冰更厚  天更冷\NThicker ice, colder weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且我比火车司机更大胆\NAnd larger balls than my chief engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说了算\NYou're the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谁拿着钱\NWho holdin' the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-大家都加入吗  -是啊\N- Everybody in? - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个谁  大块头\NYou there, big fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人们叫我帕萨姆  杜兰特先生\NThey call me Psalms, Mr. Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}帕萨姆  当然啦\NPsalms, yes, of course, Psalms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}赌注是什么\NWhat's the wager?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}火车司机过多久会跳车\NHow far across before the engineer jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得火车过不去吗\NYou don't think the train's gonna make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我赌的不是铁路\NI ain't bettin' against the railroad itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特先生  只是火车司机\NMr. Durant, just the engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然啦\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}火车司机  开车过河\NEngineer, take it across.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}恭喜  杜兰特先生\NCongratulations, Mr. Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}锅炉烧得火红  车轮飞速旋转\NRed hot boiler on ice, wheels spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不掉到冰里才怪\NWhat'd you think was gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}地狱之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}第四季  第一集
